---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Header />

<main style="max-width: 900px; margin: 80px auto; padding: 20px;">

  <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 10px;">
    IR Signal Capture & Replay System
  </h1>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 40px;">
    Interrupt-driven embedded system built on a PIC18 microcontroller for 
    capturing, decoding, and reproducing infrared remote signals with precise timing control.
  </p>

  <!-- Hardware Section -->
  <section style="margin-bottom: 60px;">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Hardware Implementation</h2>

    <img
      src="/images/ir-setup.jpg"
      alt="IR hardware setup"
      style="width: 100%; max-width: 750px; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); margin-bottom: 20px;"
    />

    <p style="color: #555;">
      Breadboard implementation featuring PIC18 microcontroller, IR receiver module,
      discrete output indicators, and signal routing for timing analysis.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Technical Highlights Section -->
  <section style="margin-bottom: 60px;">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Technical Highlights</h2>

    <div style="display: grid; gap: 15px;">
      <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
        Interrupt-driven signal capture using hardware timers
      </div>

      <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
        Timer configuration and prescaler calculation for precise pulse measurement
      </div>

      <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
        PWM-based signal reproduction matching captured waveform timing
      </div>

      <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
        Low-power sleep mode optimization and peripheral shutdown strategy
      </div>

      <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
        Datasheet-driven peripheral configuration and hardware validation
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GitHub Button -->
  <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
    <a
      href="https://github.com/JAMES-DIMARCO/JAMES-DIMARCO.github.io"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      style="
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #1d4ed8;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 500;
      "
    >
      View Source Code
    </a>
  </div>

</main>

<Footer />
